	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64370892">Does anyone think that it's going to run a few RTX 4090s?<br>
It's time to put the GPU local to the system memory, using a DMA block authorization scheme. It doesn't make any sense for all the textures/information to be coming from the drive across the box--and then go again--across the bus to the video car.</div>
